title: Untitled
content:
from itertools import product
count = 0
m = []
for p in product(sorted("КОМПЬЮТЕР"), repeat = 5):
    count += 1
    if p[0] != "Ь" and p.count("К") == 2:
        m.append(count)
print(max(m))

title: Untitled
content:
import random
from random_word import RandomWords

class shuffledWords(RandomWords):
	def __init__(self):
		self.word = ''
		self.shuffled = ''
		self.tries = 0
		super().__init__()

	def getWord(self):
		self.tries = 0
		self.word = self.get_random_word()
		self.word = 'rabbit'
		shuffled = list(self.word)
		random.shuffle(shuffled)
		self.shuffled = ''.join(shuffled)
		return self.shuffled

	def check(self,word):
		self.tries = self.tries + 1
		if str(word) == str(self.word):
			return True
		return False

sh = shuffledWords();
shuffled = sh.getWord()
while sh.tries < 4:
	s = input(f"[{sh.tries}] Solution for [{shuffled}]: ")
	if sh.check(s.strip()):
		print("You got it!")
		break
	print("Nope!")
if sh.tries >= 4:
	print('Sorry')

content:
-- Config
local TIME_PER_MESSAGE = 60

local MESSAGES = {
    "Aie caranba",
    "Defqon.1 2024 : Power Of The Tribe",
    "Le nain va-t'il se connecté ?",
    "Oh un Nain !  Shorty sort de la !",
    "Timy Bourré ?",
    "Super Mr, Super Mr.. ",
    "Smacko es ses licorne ^^",
    "Hum Az_hog..",
    "Un Noichi ? NAN",
}

-- Code
local moniteur = peripheral.wrap("top")

function obtenirDateHeureAPI()
    local response = http.get("https://worldtimeapi.org/api/timezone/Europe/Paris")
    if response then
        local data = response.readAll()
        response.close()
        local heure = textutils.unserializeJSON(data)
        local date = heure.datetime:sub(1, 10)
        local heureFormattee = heure.datetime:sub(12, 19)
        return date, heureFormattee
    else
        return "Erreur de connexion à l'API"
    end
end

function defilerTexte(texte, largeur, timetonext)

    -- Clear Debug --
    moniteur.setCursorPos(1, 5)
    moniteur.write('')
       
    local texteDefile = texte
    while #texteDefile < (largeur * 2) do
        texteDefile = texteDefile .. " " .. texte
    end

    local largeurTexte = #texteDefile
    local position = 1
    local direction = 1
    local elapsedtime = 0

    -- Debug screen --
    --moniteur.setCursorPos(1, 5)
    --moniteur.write(#texteDefile)


    while elapsedtime < timetonext do
        local texteAffiche = texteDefile:sub(position, position + largeur - 1)
        moniteur.setCursorPos(1, 4)
        moniteur.write(texteAffiche)

        position = position + direction
        if position + largeur - 1 > largeurTexte then
            position = 1
            sleep(2)
            elapsedtime = elapsedtime + 2
        else
            sleep(0.5)
            elapsedtime = elapsedtime + 0.5
        end    
        --  Debug elspsedtime --
        --  moniteur.setCursorPos(1, 5)
        --  moniteur.write(elapsedtime)
    end

end

parallel.waitForAll(
    function()
        while true do
            local date, heure = obtenirDateHeureAPI()
            moniteur.setCursorPos(1, 1)
            moniteur.write("" .. heure)
            moniteur.setCursorPos(1, 2)
            moniteur.write("" .. date)
            sleep(1)
        end
    end,
    function()
        local texteDefile = MESSAGES
        local largeurTexte, hauteur = moniteur.getSize()
        local indexTexte = 1
        local timetonext = TIME_PER_MESSAGE

        while true do
            defilerTexte(texteDefile[indexTexte], largeurTexte, timetonext)
            indexTexte = (indexTexte % #texteDefile) + 1
        end
    end
)

	fnac_cliente fecha corta no nulo,
	sex_cliente texto variable no nulo
}

cat_empleados{
	id_emo entero corto llave primaria no nulo,
	nom_emp texto variable no nulo,
	apa texto variable no nulo,
	ama texto variable no nulo,
	usu_emp texto variable no nulo,
	cve_emp texto variable no nulo
}

cat_ventas{
	id_ventas entero corto llave primaria no nulo,
	clientes_venta entero corto no nulo,
	empleado_venta entero corto no nulo,
	fecha_venta fecha corta no nulo,
	hora_benta hora no nulo
}

detalles_venta{
	id_venta_det entero corto no nulo,
	id_prod_det entero corto no nulo,
	cantidad entero no nulo
}
*/
/*
=======================================================
DISEÑO FISICO
=======================================================
*/
CREATE DATABASE TiendaModerna ON(
    name = TiendaModerna_dat,
    filename = 'C:\Program Files\Microsoft SQL Server\MSSQL16.MSSQLSERVER\MSSQL\DATA\TiendaModerna.mdf',
    SIZE = 10MB,
    maxsize = 30MB,
    filegrowth = 5MB
)
log ON(
    name = TiendaModerna_log,
    filename = 'C:\Program Files\Microsoft SQL Server\MSSQL16.MSSQLSERVER\MSSQL\DATA\TiendaModerna.ldf',
    SIZE = 5MB,
    maxsize = 30MB,
    filegrowth = 5MB
);
USE TiendaModerna
GO
 
CREATE TABLE Cat_Proveedores(
    id_prov SMALLINT PRIMARY KEY,
    nom_prov varchar(30) not null,
	tel_prov varchar(10) not null,
	mail_prov varchar(30) not null
); 
CREATE TABLE Cat_Categorias(
    id_cat SMALLINT PRIMARY KEY,
    desc_cat varchar(30) not null
);
CREATE TABLE Cat_Marcas(
    id_marca SMALLINT PRIMARY KEY,
    desc_marca varchar(30) not null
);
CREATE TABLE Cat_Productos(
    id_prod SMALLINT PRIMARY KEY,
    id_prov_prod SMALLINT not null,
    id_cate_prod SMALLINT not null,
    id_marca_prod SMALLINT not null,
    nom_prod varchar(30) not null,
	precio_prod int not null,
	cant_prod int not null,
	fec_cad_prod date not null
	constraint "id_prov_prod" foreign key(id_prov_prod)
	references Cat_Proveedores(id_prov),
	constraint "id_cate_prod" foreign key(id_cate_prod)
	references Cat_Categorias(id_cat),
	constraint "id_marca_prod" foreign key(id_marca_prod)
	references Cat_Marcas(id_marca),
);
CREATE TABLE Cat_Clientes(
    id_cliente SMALLINT PRIMARY KEY,
    nom_cliente varchar(30) not null,
	tel_cliente varchar(10) not null,
	fnac_cliente date not null,
	sex_cliente varchar(1) not null
);
CREATE TABLE Cat_Empleados(
    id_emp SMALLINT PRIMARY KEY,
    nom_emp varchar(40) not null,
    apa_emp varchar(20) not null,
    ama_emp varchar(20) not null,
	usu_emp varchar(10) not null,
	cve_emp varchar(10) not null
);
CREATE TABLE Ventas(
    id_ventas SMALLINT PRIMARY KEY,
    cliente_venta SMALLINT not null,
    empleado_venta SMALLINT not null,
    fecha_venta date not null,
	hora_venta time not null,
	constraint "cliente_venta" foreign key(cliente_venta)
	references Cat_Clientes(id_Cliente),
	constraint "empleado_venta" foreign key(empleado_venta)
	references Cat_empleados(id_emp)
);
CREATE TABLE Detalles_Venta(
	id_venta_det smallint not null,
	id_prod_det smallint not null,
	cantidad int not null,
	CONSTRAINT "id_venta_det" FOREIGN KEY(id_venta_det)
    REFERENCES Ventas(id_ventas),
	CONSTRAINT "id_prod_det" FOREIGN KEY(id_prod_det)
    REFERENCES Cat_productos(id_prod)
);

CREATE TABLE Reg_Caja(
	fecha_RegCaja date not null,
	acumulado int not null
)
/*
=======================================================
METODOS, TRIGGERS Y VISTAS
=======================================================
*/
-- Trigger para actualizar el inventario con cada venta
CREATE TRIGGER ActualizarInventarioVenta ON Detalles_Venta AFTER INSERT AS
BEGIN
    UPDATE Cat_Productos SET cant_prod = cant_prod - i.cantidad
    FROM Cat_Productos AS p INNER JOIN inserted AS i
    ON p.id_prod = i.id_prod_det;
END;
-- Trigger para actualizar el total en caja despues de cada venta
CREATE TRIGGER ActualizarCaja ON Detalles_Venta AFTER INSERT AS
BEGIN
    UPDATE Reg_Caja SET acumulado = acumulado + (precio_prod*cantidad)
    FROM Cat_Productos, inserted
    where id_prod = id_prod_det;
END;
-- Vista para productos con bajo inventario
create view viw_ProductosBajoInventario AS
	SELECT ID_Prod, nom_prod, cant_prod
	FROM cat_Productos
	WHERE cant_prod < 5;
-- Vista para productos cerca de caducar
create view viw_ProductosCercaDeCaducar AS
	SELECT ID_Prod, nom_prod, cant_prod
	FROM cat_Productos
	WHERE DATEDIFF(DAY,fec_cad_prod,GETDATE())<7
-- Crear la vista para el reporte semanal de ventas
CREATE VIEW viw_ReporteSemanal AS
SELECT
    id_ventas as Folio,
    cliente_venta as Cliente,
    empleado_venta as Empleado,
    fecha_venta as Fecha,
    id_prod_det as IdProducto,
    cantidad as Cantidad
FROM Ventas, Detalles_Venta
WHERE id_ventas = id_venta_det
and DATEPART(week, fecha_venta) = DATEPART(week, GETDATE());

title: Roblox Basic Chat Admin
content:
local commands = {}

local prefix = "!"


local function FindPlayer(name, sender)
	for i, player in pairs(game.Players:GetPlayers()) do
		if string.lower(player.Name) == name then
			return player
		elseif name == "me" then
			return sender
		end
	end

	return nil
end

local function FindTool(name)
	for i, tool in pairs(game.ServerStorage.Tools:GetChildren()) do
		if string.lower(tool.Name) == name then
			return tool
		end
	end

	return nil
end

commands.kick = function(sender, arguments)
	local kickPlayer = arguments[1]
	
	if kickPlayer then
		local player = FindPlayer(kickPlayer, sender)

		if player then
			player:kick(sender.Name.." has kicked you from this game.")
		end
	end
end

commands.give = function(sender, arguments)
	local item = arguments[1]

	if item then
		local Tool = FindTool(item)
		if Tool then
			local Clone = Tool:Clone()
			Clone.Parent = sender.Backpack
		end
	end
end


commands.tp = function(sender, arguments)
	local PlayerToTP = arguments[1]
	local PlayerTPTo = arguments[2]

	if PlayerToTP and PlayerTPTo then
		local TpPlayer = FindPlayer(PlayerToTP, sender)
		local Pos = FindPlayer(PlayerTPTo, sender)
		if TpPlayer and Pos then
			TpPlayer.Character:PivotTo(Pos.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame + Vector3.new(0, 5, 0))
		end
	end
end

commands.speed = function(sender, arguments)
	local speedPlayer = arguments[1]
	local speed = arguments[2]

	
	if speedPlayer and speed then
		local player = FindPlayer(speedPlayer, sender)

		if player then
			player.Character.Humanoid.WalkSpeed = speed
		end
	end
end

commands.invisible = function(sender, arguments)
	local invisiblePlayer = arguments[1]


	if invisiblePlayer then
		local player = FindPlayer(invisiblePlayer, sender)

		if player then
			local character = player.Character
			if character then
				for i, part in pairs(character:GetDescendants()) do
					if part:IsA("Decal") then
						part.Transparency = 1
					end
					if part:IsA("BasePart") then
						part.Transparency = 1
					end
				end
			end
		end
	end
end

commands.visible = function(sender, arguments)
	local visiblePlayer = arguments[1]


	if visiblePlayer then
		local player = FindPlayer(visiblePlayer, sender)

		if player then
			local character = player.Character
			if character then
				for i, part in pairs(character:GetDescendants()) do
					if part:IsA("Decal") then
						part.Transparency = 0
					end
					if part:IsA("BasePart") then
						if part.Name == "HumanoidRootPart" then
							part.Transparency = 1
						else
							part.Transparency = 0
						end
					
					end
				end
			end
		end
	end
end

commands.highlight = function(sender, arguments)
	local highlightPlayer = arguments[1]

	if highlightPlayer then
		local Player = FindPlayer(highlightPlayer, sender)
		if Player then
			local character = Player.Character
			if character then
				local highlight = Instance.new("Highlight", character)
			end
		end
	end
end

commands.kill = function(sender, arguments)
	local killPlayer = arguments[1]

	if killPlayer then
		local Player = FindPlayer(killPlayer, sender)
		if Player then
			local character = Player.Character
			if character then
				character.Humanoid.Health = 0
			end
		end
	end
end

commands.explode = function(sender, arguments)
	local explodePlayer = arguments[1]

	if explodePlayer then
		local Player = FindPlayer(explodePlayer, sender)
		if Player then
			local character = Player.Character
			if character then
				local explosion = Instance.new("Explosion", character)
				explosion.Position = character.HumanoidRootPart.Position
			end
		end
	end
end


game.Players.PlayerAdded:Connect(function(player)
	player.Chatted:Connect(function(message, recipient)
		message = string.lower(message)
		
		local splitString = message:split(" ")
		
		local slashCommand = splitString[1]
		
		local cmd = slashCommand:split(prefix)
		
		local cmdName = cmd[2]
		
		if commands[cmdName] then
			
			local arguments = {}
			
			for i = 2, #splitString, 1  do
				table.insert(arguments, splitString[i])
			end
			
			commands[cmdName](player, arguments)
		end
		
	end)
end)

title: floorController
content:
globalPort = 5296
floorName = "test1"

modem = peripheral.find("modem")
bottom = peripheral.wrap("bottom")
top = peripheral.wrap("top")

modem.open(globalPort)

serverId = 0
status = {cur = top.list()[1].nbt, name=floorName, expected = top.list()[1].nbt}

    

commands = {
    alert = function(input)
        assert(type(input) == "string", "alert expects a string for its input")
        print("ALERT: " .. input)
        return true
    end,

    init = function(id)
	assert(type(id) == "number", "init expects a number for its input")
	print("initializing ------------------------------")
	serverId = id
	updateStatus(true)
    end,

    updateDb = function(db)
	assert(type(db) == "table", "updateDb expects a table for its input")
	status = db[os.computerID()]
    end,

    prep = function()
	updateStatus(true)
	commandRunner("ready", serverId, {})
    end

}


function commandParser(cList)
    event, side, channel, replyChannel, message, distance = os.pullEvent("modem_message")
    print(textutils.serialise(message))
    if cList[message.cmd] ~= nil and message.args ~= nil then
	if message.tgt ~= os.computerID() and message.tgt ~= (-1) then 
		print("not me")
		return
	end

        ran, err = pcall(cList[message.cmd], table.unpack(message.args))
        if not ran then
            print(("Error in \"%s\": %s"):format(message.cmd, err))
        end
    else
        print(("No command named \"%s\" found"):format(message.cmd))
    end
end

function commandRunner(command, target, arguments)
	assert(type(command) == "string", "commandRunner expects a string for its input \"command\"")
	assert(type(target) == "number", "commandRunner expects a number for its input \"target\"")
	assert(type(arguments) == "table", "commandRunner expects a table for its input \"arguments\"")
	modem.transmit(5296,5296, {cmd=command, tgt=target, args=arguments})
end


function updateStatus(update)
	cur = "empty"
	for key,value in pairs(top.list()) do
		if cur == "empty" then
			cur = value.nbt
		else
			cur = "multiple"
		end
	end
	diff = status["cur"] ~= cur
	status["cur"] = cur
	if diff or update then commandRunner("updateStatus", serverId, {os.computerID(), status}) end
end


function checkNetwork()
	commandParser(commands)
end
function checkStatus()
	print(textutils.serialise(status))

	for key,value in pairs(top.list()) do
		if value.nbt ~= status.expected then
			top.pushItems("bottom", key)
		end
	end

	for key,value in pairs(bottom.list()) do
		if value.nbt == status.expected then
			bottom.pushItems("top", key)
		end
	end
	updateStatus(false)

	sleep(1)
end
    


while true do
        parallel.waitForAny(checkStatus, checkNetwork) 
end

local function MainRunner()
	local script = Instance.new('Script', ScreenGui)

	local frame = script.Parent:WaitForChild("Frame")
	local Template = script.Parent:WaitForChild("Template")
	
	local BIG_NUM = 10000000000000 -- to prevent floating point error

	local function scale(num)
		return num * BIG_NUM
	end

	local function rescale(num)
		return num / BIG_NUM
	end
	
	local function GetChanceLeft()
		local chance = 100
		for i, v in pairs(frame:WaitForChild("ScrollingFrame"):GetChildren()) do
			if v:IsA("TextLabel") then
				local scaledchance = scale(chance)
				chance = rescale((scaledchance - scale(v:GetAttribute("Chance"))))
				
			end
		end
		return chance
	end
	
	local function countDecimalPlaces(num)
		local strNum = tostring(num)
		local decimalPos = string.find(strNum, "%.")
		if not decimalPos then
			return 0
		end
		return #strNum - decimalPos
	end
	
	local function ReturnHighestDecimalPlace()
		local last = 0
		for i, v in pairs(frame:WaitForChild("ScrollingFrame"):GetChildren()) do
			if v:IsA("TextLabel") then
				local chance = v:GetAttribute("Chance")
				local DecimalPlaces = countDecimalPlaces(chance)
				if DecimalPlaces > last then
					last = DecimalPlaces
				end
			end
		end
		return last
	end
	
	frame:WaitForChild("Add").MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		local NameValue = frame:WaitForChild("NameValue").Text
		local ChanceValue = frame:WaitForChild("ChanceValue").Text
		if tonumber(ChanceValue) == nil then warn("Invalid chance!") return end
		if tostring(NameValue) == nil then warn("Invalid name!") return end
		ChanceValue = tonumber(ChanceValue)
		NameValue = tostring(NameValue)
		
		if GetChanceLeft() < ChanceValue then
			warn("Not enough chance left!")
			return
		end 
		if ChanceValue < 0 then
			warn("why?")
			return
		end
		local Clone = Template:Clone()
		Clone.LayoutOrder = -(math.floor(ChanceValue))
		Clone.Text = string.format('"%s" Chance: %s',NameValue,tostring(ChanceValue).."%")
		Clone:SetAttribute("Chance",ChanceValue)
		Clone.Visible = true
		Clone:WaitForChild("Delete").MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
			Clone:Destroy()
		end)
		Clone.Parent = frame:WaitForChild("ScrollingFrame")
	end)
	
	frame:WaitForChild("Done").MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		if GetChanceLeft() ~= 0 then
			warn("Chance left is not at 0!")
			return
		end
		
		local HighestDecimalPlace = ReturnHighestDecimalPlace()
		local HighestNumberPossible = 10^HighestDecimalPlace
	
		local Source = string.format("local Selected = nil\nlocal RandomNumber = math.random(1,%s)\n", HighestNumberPossible * 100)
		local lowerLimit = 0
		local upperLimit = 0
	
		local isFirst = true
		for _, child in ipairs(frame:WaitForChild("ScrollingFrame"):GetChildren()) do
			if child:IsA("TextLabel") then
				local chance = child:GetAttribute("Chance")
				upperLimit = upperLimit + (chance * 10^HighestDecimalPlace)
	
				if isFirst then
					Source = Source .. string.format(
						"if RandomNumber > %s and RandomNumber <= %s then\n\tSelected = \"%s\"\n",
						lowerLimit,
						upperLimit,
						child.Text:match("\"(.-)\"")
					)
					isFirst = false
				else
					Source = Source .. string.format(
						"elseif RandomNumber > %s and RandomNumber <= %s then\n\tSelected = \"%s\"\n",
						lowerLimit,
						upperLimit,
						child.Text:match("\"(.-)\"")
					)
				end
	
				lowerLimit = upperLimit
			end
		end
	
		Source = Source .. "end\n"
		local new = Instance.new("Script")
		new.Source = Source
		new.Name = "New Random Choice Code"
		new.Parent = workspace
		game:GetService("Selection"):Set({new})
	end)
	local go = true
	frame:WaitForChild("Exit").MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		go = false
		script.Parent:Destroy()
	end)
	
	frame:WaitForChild("Reset").MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		for i, v in pairs(frame.ScrollingFrame:GetChildren()) do
			if v:IsA("TextLabel") then
				v:Destroy()
			end
		end
	end)
	
	frame:WaitForChild("ChanceLeft").MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		frame.ChanceValue.Text = tostring(GetChanceLeft())
	end)
	
	while go do
		frame:WaitForChild("ChanceLeft").Text = "Chance Left: "..tostring(GetChanceLeft()).."%"
		frame:WaitForChild("ChanceUsed").Text = "Chance Used: "..tostring(100 - GetChanceLeft()).."%"
		task.wait(.2)
	end
end
coroutine.wrap(MainRunner)()

title: aimbot
content:
local camera = game.Workspace.CurrentCamera
local players = game:GetService("Players")

local function findNearestPlayer()
    local nearestPlayer = nil
    local minDistance = math.huge
    local cameraPosition = camera.CFrame.p

    for _, player in pairs(players:GetPlayers()) do
        if player.Character and player.Character:FindFirstChild("HumanoidRootPart") then
            local playerPosition = player.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position
            local distance = (cameraPosition - playerPosition).Magnitude

            if distance < minDistance then
                nearestPlayer = player
                minDistance = distance
            end
        end
    end

    return nearestPlayer
end

local function updateCamera()
    local nearestPlayer = findNearestPlayer()

    if nearestPlayer then
        local playerPosition = nearestPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position
        local lookAt = CFrame.new(camera.CFrame.p, playerPosition)

        -- Adjust camera position and orientation
        camera.CFrame = lookAt
    end
end

-- Update the camera at a regular interval
while true do
    updateCamera()
    wait(0.1) -- Adjust the update rate as needed
end

local function destroyDrop(drop)
	task.spawn(function()
		-- zapamiętaj obszar z którego pochodzi drop
		local oldParent = drop.Parent
		-- przenieś drop do folderu despawnedDrops
		drop.Parent = despawnedDrops
		-- poczekaj 4 sek
		wait(4)
		-- ustaw życie dropu na wartość maksymalną
		drop.CurrentPoints.Value = drop.MaxPoints.Value
		-- wstaw drop z powrotem do obszaru z którego pochodzi
		drop.Parent = oldParent
	end)
end
local function updateDamage()
	-- odczytaj aktualną listę petów gracza
	local playerPets = GetPlayerPets()
	-- pętla przechodząca po wszystkich petach gracza
	for _, pet in ipairs(playerPets) do
		-- ustaw ustaw target na cel ataku peta
		local target = pet.Attack.Value
		-- jeśli cel jest ustawiony (nie jest nil)
		if target then
			-- ustaw zmienną drop jako rodzica atakowego elementu
			-- (atakujemy PrimaryPart/model 3D naszego dropa)
			local drop = target.Parent
			-- ustaw zmienną currentPoints an aktualne punkty (życia) dropu
			local currentPoints = drop.CurrentPoints
			-- odejmij od punktów życia dropa wartość ataku peta
			-- jeśli wartość spadła poniżej zera - ustaw ją na z0
			currentPoints.Value = math.max(currentPoints.Value - pet.Damage.Value, 0)
			
			-- jeśli aktualne życie dropu jest równe 0:
			
			if currentPoints.Value == 0 then
				-- ustaw cel ataku petów jako pusty
				attackTarget.Value = nil
				SetAttackTarget(nil)
				-- usuń ten drop z planszy (za pomocą funkcji)
				destroyDrop(drop)
			end
		end
	end
end


-- funkcja aktualizująca paski życia dropów na scenie
local function updateDropDisplay()
	-- pętla przechodząca po elementach w folderze drops
	for _, drop in pairs(drops:GetDescendants()) do
		-- jeśli obiekt jest modelem - czyli faktycznym dropem
		if drop:IsA("Model") then
			-- znajdź w dropie element o nazwie Display (jest to BilboardGui)
			local display = drop:FindFirstChild("Display")
			-- zmienna bar wskazuje na pasek w elemencie display
			local bar = display.Background.Bar
			-- zmienna displayText wskazuje na tekst z liczbą życia
			local displayText displayText = display.Background.Amount
			-- ustaw tekst displayText na wartość aktualnych punktów życia dropu
			displayText.Text = tostring(drop.CurrentPoints.Value)
			-- animacja paska z obecnej długości do tej 
			-- przedstawianej przez punkty życia dropu
			bar:TweenSize(
				UDim2.fromScale(drop.CurrentPoints.Value / drop.MaxPoints.Value, 1),
				Enum.EasingDirection.Out,
				Enum.EasingStyle.Sine,
				0.3)
		end
	end
end

task.spawn(function()
	while task.wait(1) do
		-- uruchom aktualizację obrażeń
		updateDamage()
		-- uruchom aktualizację pasków życia dropóW
		updateDropDisplay()
	end
end)

modem = peripheral.find("modem")
modem.open(5296)
db = {}

    

commands = {
    alert = function(input)
        assert(type(input) == "string", "helloWorld expects a string for its input")
        print("ALERT: " .. input)
        return true
    end,
    
    updateStatus = function(id, dataObj)
        assert(type(id) == "number", "updateStatus expects an int for \"id\"")
        assert(type(dataObj) == "table", "updateStatus expects a table for \"dataObj\"")
        print(id)
        db[id] = dataObj
    end
}


function commandRunner(event, side, channel, replyChannel, message, distance)
    print(textutils.serialise(message))
    if commands[message.cmd] ~= nil and message.args ~= nil then
        ran, err = pcall(commands[message.cmd], table.unpack(message.args))
        if not ran then
            print(("Error in \"%s\": %s"):format(message.cmd, err))
        end
    else
        print(("No command named \"%s\" found"):format(message.cmd))
    end
end
    


while true do
	commandRunner(os.pullEvent("modem_message"))
            
end

title: Command Base
content:
globalPort = 5296

modem = peripheral.find("modem")
modem.open(globalPort)
db = {}

    

commands = {
    alert = function(input)
        assert(type(input) == "string", "helloWorld expects a string for its input")
        print("ALERT: " .. input)
        return true
    end,
}


function commandParser(event, side, channel, replyChannel, message, distance)
    print(textutils.serialise(message))
    if commands[message.cmd] ~= nil and message.args ~= nil then
        ran, err = pcall(commands[message.cmd], table.unpack(message.args))
        if not ran then
            print(("Error in \"%s\": %s"):format(message.cmd, err))
        end
    else
        print(("No command named \"%s\" found"):format(message.cmd))
    end
end

function commandRunner(command, target, arguments)
	assert(type(command) == "string", "commandRunner expects a string for its input \"command\"")
	assert(type(target) == "number", "commandRunner expects a number for its input \"target\"")
	assert(type(arguments) == "table", "commandRunner expects a table for its input \"arguments\"")
	modem.transmit(5296,5296, {cmd=command, tgt=target, args=arguments})
end
    


while true do
	commandParser(os.pullEvent("modem_message"))
            
end
